tools.gsf.navigation

Class SimpleAssetNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • tools.gsf.navigation.SimpleAssetNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AssetNode, Node<AssetNode>

    public class SimpleAssetNode
extends Object
implements AssetNode
    Simple node, representing an asset, that can be populated with asset data. Not all attributes of the asset are necessarily loaded into this node. Many convenience methods exist for retrieving node attribute data.
    Since:
    2016-07-06
    Author:
    Tony Field
